Key changes vs the current AppShell:
1. `<AgentSidebar />` is replaced by `AnimatePresence` + `sidebarSlot.body`
2. The inline `<AgentIdentityChip ... /> <div className="flex-1" /> <CommandPaletteTrigger />` is replaced by `AnimatePresence` + `headerSlot.content`
3. The `header` element's `style` prop now reads `headerSlot.borderStyle` instead of the inline conditional
4. `SidebarTrigger` and `Separator` remain outside AnimatePresence (static chrome)
5. `SidebarFooter` and `SidebarRail` remain outside AnimatePresence (static chrome)

### Animation Specification

| Property                  | Value                                               |
| ------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| Animation type            | Opacity cross-fade                                  |
| Duration                  | 100ms (0.1)                                         |
| Easing                    | Linear (default for opacity)                        |
| AnimatePresence mode      | `wait` (old exits before new enters)                |
| `initial` on first render | `false` (no animation on page load)                 |
| Reduced motion            | Respected via existing `<MotionConfig reducedMotion="user">` |

